---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer class="border-t border-gray-800 py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-black">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-4">合同会社 TECH-i</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
          テクノロジーを、貴社の「右腕」に。Webシステム・アプリ開発、ITコンサルティング、モダンWebサイト制作、業務効率化・DX支援。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-4">リンク</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a
              href="#home"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 transition-colors">Home</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="#about"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 transition-colors"
              >About</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="#services"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 transition-colors"
              >Services</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="#company"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 transition-colors"
              >Company</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="#contact"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 transition-colors"
              >Contact</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-4">お問い合わせ</h3>
        <a
          href="mailto:r.takeuchi@tech-i.net"
          class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 transition-colors text-sm"
        >
          r.takeuchi@tech-i.net
        </a>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          GitHub:
          <a
            href="https://github.com/TECH-i-main"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="underline text-gray-300"
          >
            https://github.com/TECH-i-main
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="border-t border-gray-800 pt-8 text-center text-gray-500 text-sm"
    >
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} TECH-i LLC. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
